    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348250/extras/9b973c93b38e84747a71100448a25f8f.avif?t=1772187754\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348250/extras_big/9b973c93b38e84747a71100448a25f8f.avif?t=1772187754 width=800 height=185 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348250/extras/a8b0648c5260b45acf183e29fc5a272d.avif?t=1772187754\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348250/extras_big/a8b0648c5260b45acf183e29fc5a272d.avif?t=1772187754 width=800 height=88 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348250/extras/ac85adbc94c2c10edf7d598a8d9f3f05.poster.avif?t=1772187754\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348250/extras/ac85adbc94c2c10edf7d598a8d9f3f05.webm?t=1772187754\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348250/extras/ac85adbc94c2c10edf7d598a8d9f3f05.mp4?t=1772187754\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到生肖世界。在这里扮演动物之灵，挑战现有的十二生肖，冲击第十三生肖的宝座。您将扮演无畏的挑战者，使用独特能力，征服各式试炼，获得最终胜利。<br>  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>四名挑战者，各具特色</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >目前已有多位角色供玩家选择：迅若雷霆的狐狸；刀尖起舞的乌鸦；撼天动地的熊猫。选择你中意的动物，创造独特的战斗流派，踏上胜利之路！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>无限挑战，愈战愈强</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348250/extras/3f601392dfa8322d1caa32213ec41641.poster.avif?t=1772187754\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348250/extras/3f601392dfa8322d1caa32213ec41641.webm?t=1772187754\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348250/extras/3f601392dfa8322d1caa32213ec41641.mp4?t=1772187754\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每位动物之灵都有独特的能力与深度成长系统。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >试炼过程中，玩家可以解锁强大的加成效果，还能获得如卷轴、金砧等奖励。尝试不同技能搭配，击败已有生肖，在成为第十三生肖的试炼路上披荆斩棘。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>独乐乐，也能众乐乐</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏支持单人战斗模式和多人合作模式。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>单人模式</strong></u>：在单人模式中磨炼技术，直面生肖试炼，让您的战斗技巧臻于完美。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348250/extras/86637aa858b6147f5fa0dbd0a16c382f.poster.avif?t=1772187754\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348250/extras/86637aa858b6147f5fa0dbd0a16c382f.webm?t=1772187754\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348250/extras/86637aa858b6147f5fa0dbd0a16c382f.mp4?t=1772187754\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>合作模式（2-4名玩家)</strong></u>：与好友合作，共闯试炼。你们会面对更凶狠的敌人、更强大的Boss，甚至某些可能导致内斗的诱惑，好友间的战术与友情都将受到考验。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348250/extras/a9e320fc794b2d5b0d2f1e2b69a6eda9.poster.avif?t=1772187754\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348250/extras/a9e320fc794b2d5b0d2f1e2b69a6eda9.webm?t=1772187754\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348250/extras/a9e320fc794b2d5b0d2f1e2b69a6eda9.mp4?t=1772187754\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>收获游戏乐趣，不论经验</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论是初尝动作游戏的新手玩家，还是经验丰富的老手，都可以在13th Zodiac中体验到乐趣。由浅入深的考验，多样独特的敌人，以及强大的特色 BOSS。每个人都能在这场不断进化的动作Roguelike冒险中磨炼自己的技术。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348250/extras/07e472203c068233e5ae89e29b35d343.poster.avif?t=1772187754\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348250/extras/07e472203c068233e5ae89e29b35d343.webm?t=1772187754\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348250/extras/07e472203c068233e5ae89e29b35d343.mp4?t=1772187754\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你能通过所有试炼，成为传说中的第十三位生肖吗？</strong></p>",
